-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} {{small|Blaisdell Center Arena, [[Honolulu, Hawaii]], U.S.}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{small|For [[list of WBA world champions#SuperFeatherweight|WBA]] and lineal super featherweight titles}}\n|-\n|32\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|29\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Maneul Rodriguez\n|TKO\n|6 (?)\n|December 13, 1975\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|31\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|28\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PAN}} Diego Alcala\n|PTS\n|10\n|October 11, 1975\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|30\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|27\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|USA}} Ahmet Tosci\n|KO\n|2 (10)\n|September 1, 1975\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|29\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|26\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|ARG}} Victor Echegaray\n|PTS\n|10\n|July 28, 1975\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|28\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|25\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|DOM}} Jose Pena\n|PTS\n|10\n|April 12, 1975\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|27\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|24\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|MEX}} Memo Cruz\n|PTS\n|10\n|November 15, 1974\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|26\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|23\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|DOM}} Ezequiel Cocoa Sanchez\n|PTS\n|10\n|July 29, 1974\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|PUR}} {{small|[[San Juan, Puerto Rico|San Juan]], Puerto Rico}}\n|\n|-\n|25\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|22\u20133\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|VEN}} Gustavo Briceno\n|KO\n|10 (12)\n|July 15, 1974\n|style=\"text