TTO}}\n** [[Port of Spain]] (Embassy)\n*{{USA}}\n** [[Washington, D.C.]] ([[German Embassy, Washington, D.C.|Embassy]])\n** [[Atlanta, Georgia|Atlanta]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Boston, Massachusetts|Boston]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Chicago]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Houston, Texas|Houston]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Los Angeles, California|Los Angeles]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Miami, Florida|Miami]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[New York City|New York]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[San Francisco, California|San Francisco]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Uruguay}}\n** [[Montevideo]] (Embassy)\n*{{VEN}}\n** [[Caracas]] (Embassy)\n\n==Asia==\n*{{Flag|Afghanistan}}\n** [[Kabul]] (Embassy) (currently closed)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.afghanistan.diplo.de/Vertretung/afghanistan/en/Startseite.html|title=German Missions in Afghanistan - Home|website=www.afghanistan.diplo.de|language=en|access-date=2017-06-03}}</ref>\n** [[Mazar-e-Sharif]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Armenia}}\n** [[Yerevan]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Azerbaijan}}\n** [[Baku]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Bahrain}}\n** [[Manama]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Bangladesh}}\n** [[Dhaka]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Brunei}}\n** [[Bandar Seri Begawan]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Cambodia}}\n** [[Phnom Penh]] (Embassy)\n*{{CHN}}\n** [[Beijing]] (Embassy)\n** [[Chengdu]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Guangzhou]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Hong Kong]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Shanghai]] ([[List of German Consuls-General in Shanghai|Consulate-General]])\n** [[Shenyang]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Georgia}}\n** [[Tbilisi]] (Embassy)\n*{{IND}}\n** [[New Delhi]] (Embassy)\n** [[Bangalore]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Chennai]] ([[Consulate General of the Federal Republic of Germany in Chennai|Consulate-General]])\n** [[Kolkata]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Mumbai]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{IDN}}\n** [[Jakarta]] (Embassy)\n*{{IRN}}\n** [[Tehran]] (Embassy)\n*{{IRQ}}\n** [[Baghdad]] (Embassy)\n** [[Erbil]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Israel}}\n** [[Tel Aviv]] ([[Emba