assy)\n*{{Flag|Cambodia}}\n** [[Phnom Penh]] (Embassy)\n*{{CHN}}\n** [[Beijing]] (Embassy)\n** [[Chengdu]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Guangzhou]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Hong Kong]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Shanghai]] ([[List of German Consuls-General in Shanghai|Consulate-General]])\n** [[Shenyang]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Georgia}}\n** [[Tbilisi]] (Embassy)\n*{{IND}}\n** [[New Delhi]] (Embassy)\n** [[Bangalore]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Chennai]] ([[Consulate General of the Federal Republic of Germany in Chennai|Consulate-General]])\n** [[Kolkata]] (Consulate-General)\n** [[Mumbai]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{IDN}}\n** [[Jakarta]] (Embassy)\n*{{IRN}}\n** [[Tehran]] (Embassy)\n*{{IRQ}}\n** [[Baghdad]] (Embassy)\n** [[Erbil]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Israel}}\n** [[Tel Aviv]] ([[Embassy of Germany, Tel Aviv|Embassy]])\n*{{JPN}}\n** [[Tokyo]] (Embassy)\n** [[Osaka]] ([[Umeda Sky Building|Consulate-General]])\n*{{Flag|Jordan}}\n** [[Amman]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Kazakhstan}}\n** [[Nur-Sultan]] (Embassy)\n** [[Almaty]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{Flag|Kuwait}}\n** [[Kuwait City]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Kyrgyzstan}}\n** [[Bishkek]] (Embassy)\n*{{LAO}}\n** [[Vientiane]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Lebanon}}\n** [[Beirut]] (Embassy)\n*{{MYS}}\n** [[Kuala Lumpur]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Mongolia}}\n** [[Ulan Bator]] (Embassy)\n*{{MMR}}\n** [[Yangon]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Nepal}}\n** [[Kathmandu]] (Embassy)\n*{{PRK}}\n** [[Pyongyang]] (Embassy)\n*{{OMN}}\n** [[Muscat, Oman|Muscat]] (Embassy)\n*{{PAK}}\n** [[Islamabad]] (Embassy)\n** [[Karachi]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{PSE}}\n** [[Ramallah]] (Representative Office)\n*{{PHI}}\n** [[Manila]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Qatar}}\n** [[Doha]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Saudi Arabia}}\n** [[Riyadh]] (Embassy)\n** [[Jeddah]] (Consulate-General)\n*{{SGP}}\n** [[Singapore]] (Embassy)\n*{{KOR}}\n** [[Seoul]] (Embassy)\n*{{Flag|Sri Lanka}}\n** [[Colombo]] (Embassy)\n*{{TWN}}\n** [[Taipei]] ([[German Institute Taipei]])\n*{{Flag|Tajikistan}}\n** [[Dushanbe]] (Embassy)\n